{"tid":1084950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"結局總是不盡人意","createTime":"2019-03-30T18:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:20:46.000Z","uid":98360,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e839c813de1bdd2a39aacdefb0a268bba195bc98","tid":1084950,"uid":98360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:54:59.000Z","msg":"見到你，很想擁抱你，可惜我沒勇氣，害怕你只會受更大的傷害，我不忍心，但我沒打算放下，我會一個人獨自藏於心底。<br />\n<br />\n沒有你，我快樂嗎？從不，但沒有我，你會得到快樂。我再沒勇氣在你面前說這三個字，可是都是真的，我愛你。<br />\n<br />\n最矛盾的心情，就是放手讓心愛的人走自己的路。"},{"pid":"ebd74e31f37330d393db8d232f4bb684197c37fd","tid":1084950,"uid":95637,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:55:52.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"fc59439698eb78cbe781d5493a3bef5e847b413b","tid":1084950,"uid":6097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:22:32.000Z","msg":"是但啦 人總有緣盡的時候 開心過就好了"},{"pid":"79b7446e57149cecc8df18282e5aafa1fc0142f7","tid":1084950,"uid":157363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:26:40.000Z","msg":"無佢，你從不快樂。但有佢你就快樂？問2句就話好大壓力踩鋼線，咁係快樂？快樂地痛？"},{"pid":"ee16dbc81872d508f279893b3651ecde83b871ce","tid":1084950,"uid":88871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"好希望係前女友同我講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33503e479a32d990ecb2b37b8bd610b6dd26a948","tid":1084950,"uid":157363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠"}]}